<% title 'Reggae Dub Ska' %>
<div class="ui container genre-desc">
  <h1>REGGAE</h1>
  <p>John Peel had a profound love of reggae and was one of the foremost promoters of black music throughout the majority of his Radio 1 career. Many discovered Bob Marley, Culture, Misty, Steel Pulse, Dr Alimantado, Lee 'Scratch' Perry, Scientist, and The Mad Professor through John, not forgetting Linton Kwesi Johnson, Benjamin Zephaniah, the late Michael Smith and so many more.</p>
</div>
<div class="ui container">
   <ul class="genre-list">
    <% @sessions.each do |s| %>
      <div class="genre-list-item" >
        <div>
          <%= react_component("SessionListItem", { session: s }) %>
        </div>
        <%= link_to toggle_favorite_session_path(s), remote: true, method: :post do %>
          <div class="like-icon " data-id="<%= s.id %>">
            <%= render 'like_button' %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <%end%>
  </ul>
</div>
